  "prompt": "What are the various Incarnations of Lord Vishnu and what is going to be the last Incarnation of Lord Vishnu?",
  "response": "In Hinduism, Lord Vishnu is believed to have taken several incarnations (avatars) to restore cosmic order and protect dharma (righteousness) whenever it is threatened by evil. The most widely recognized list of these incarnations is known as the \"Dashavatara,\" which comprises ten principal avatars:\n\n1. **Matsya** (The Fish) - Rescued the sage Manu and the sacred texts during a great flood.\n2. **Kurma** (The Tortoise) - Supported Mount Mandara during the churning of the ocean (Samudra Manthan) to obtain nectar of immortality.\n3. **Varaha** (The Boar) - Rescued the Earth (personified as the goddess Bhudevi) from the demon Hiranyaksha.\n4. **Narasimha** (The Man-Lion) - Appeared to protect his devotee Prahlada and to defeat the demon king Hiranyakashipu.\n5. **Vamana** (The Dwarf) - Took three steps to reclaim the universe from the demon king Bali.\n6. **Parashurama** (The Warrior with an Axe) - A Brahmin warrior who eliminated the corrupt Kshatriya rulers.\n7. **Rama** (The Prince of Ayodhya) - The hero of the Ramayana, who defeated the demon king Ravana to rescue his wife Sita.\n8. **Krishna** (The Divine Cowherd) - A key figure in the Mahabharata and the Bhagavad Gita, who played a crucial role in various events, including the Kurukshetra War.\n9. **Buddha** (The Enlightened One) - Often included in some traditions as an avatar to bring compassion and enlightenment.\n10. **Kalki** (The Future Warrior) - The prophesied future incarnation who will appear riding a white horse, wielding a sword, to end the current age of darkness and corruption (Kali Yuga) and to restore righteousness.\n\nThe last incarnation of Lord Vishnu, as per the Hindu belief, is **Kalki**, who is expected to appear at the end of the current age of Kali Yuga. He will bring an end to adharma (unrighteousness) and establish a new era of righteousness or Satya Yuga, heralding the eventual restoration of balance in the universe.",
